{"tid":652322,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(猜拿又贏之人加我減)Apple減價","createTime":"2018-05-03T18:34:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T18:34:23.000Z","uid":34013,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2db3f68b4685b1bcb729216d66eca3f6f856e70f","tid":652322,"uid":34013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T18:34:23.000Z","msg":"調整增值稅率 大陸 Apple Store 全線產品價格下調<br />\n<br />\n大陸的 Apple Store，無論是網上還是實體店，日前都出現全線調低價格的現象。不過這跟智能手機的整體銷量下滑，Apple 需要透過減價促銷完全無關，而是中國稅務總局之前發出調整增值稅率的通知，在今年 5 月 1 日起開始生效所致。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}